pma:database.name: ravaisi
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `orders` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `order_string` text NOT NULL, `date_time` datetime NOT NULL, `order_table` text NOT NULL, `price` float NOT NULL, `order_index` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT 1, `loaded` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `printed` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `closed` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=342 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `products` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` text NOT NULL, `price` double NOT NULL, `category` text NOT NULL, `toppings` text NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), UNIQUE KEY `name` (`name`) USING HASH ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=35 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `toppings` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` text NOT NULL, `extra` double NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), UNIQUE KEY `name` (`name`) USING HASH ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=18 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;
